│ against replacing allocas. The resulting IR violates intrinsic constraints    │
│ before dead code cleanup removes the now-reachable block.                     │
│                                                                               │
│ 3. Root Cause Analysis:                                                       │
│ PredicateInfo plus handlePredicate can (under an equality branch) merge a     │
