│ replacement already polluted IR. The minimal and reliable fix is to prevent   │
│ tryToReplaceWithConstant from substituting AllocaInst results with constants  │
│ (other than poison, which verifier allows). This preserves intrinsic operand  │
│ invariants and avoids introducing incorrect control-flow folding based on the │
│ fabricated constant address.                                                  │
